title: The Big Book of Civil War Sites
description:
The Big Book of Civil War Sites: From Fort Sumter to Appomattox, a Visitor's Guide to the History, Personalities, and Places of America's Battlefields - Cynthia Parzych (ed.) [epub]

The Big Book of Civil War Sites is the consummate travel reference for Americaâ€™s Civil War battlefields.
